Isabelle Kalihangabo Umunyapolitiki W'umunyamategeko Akaba  n'Umunyamabanga mukigo kigihugu Cy'iperereza Mu [[Rwanda]] (RIB).

Umwanya ariho kuva 2018.<ref>https://www.rib.gov.rw/index.php?id=23</ref>

== Umwuga. ==

Kalihangabo umunyamategeko wabonye impanya bushobozi Mu mategeko yakuye muri kaminuza y'u[[Rwanda]].

Yabonye Kandi impanya bushobozi yikiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza yakuye muri kaminuza ya Queen Mary University muri London mubijyanye Namategeko Y'ubucucuzi mpuza mahanga.

2000 inkugeza 2004 Isabelle Kalihangabo Yakoze Mu Rukiko rwikirenge rw'URwanda migice gishinzwe  inkiko Gacaca.

2004 Isabelle Kalihangabo yahawe Umwanya wumucanza murukiko rukuru rw'URwanda.

2007 Isabelle yagizwe umwunganizi mu Mategeko muri Minisiteri yubutabera<ref>https://www.degruyter.com/document/doi/10.1515/9780822373568-003/pdf</ref>

Muri Werurwe 2014 Isabelle  Nyuma yo kubona ubushobozi bwe yazamuwe muntera ajyira umunyamabanga uhoraho nuhagarariye amategeko muri Minisiteri yubutabera y'uRwanda.


